    <h1>Through-the-Line (TTL) Marketing</h1>
    <p class="description">An <strong>integrated advertising approach</strong> that combines above-the-line mass-reach media (TV, radio, outdoor) with below-the-line targeted tactics (email, PPC, in-store) in a single coordinated campaign — bridging brand building and direct response.</p>
