            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Digital marketing spans both. Display advertising and YouTube pre-rolls with broad targeting are closer to ATL. Search ads, retargeting, and email campaigns with defined audience segments are BTL. Most digital-first brands run TTL campaigns by default, even if they don't use that label — they combine awareness-stage social and content marketing with conversion-stage search and email.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
